Text:
That serial key has been banned for nearly a year now.
use one of the keys listed at the bottom.

If you already have xp vlk with a cd-key that has gone bad, do the following:

1: Create a new text document called "ChangeVLKey.txt" without quotes
2: Open the file and paste the following: (This is Microsoft's own coded script BTW)

' 
' WMI Script - ChangeVLKey.vbs
'
' This script changes the product key on the computer
'
'***************************************************************************

ON ERROR RESUME NEXT


if Wscript.arguments.countrun then type: c:\changevlkeysp1.vbs *****-*****-*****-*****-*****
((( Replace *****-*****-*****-*****-***** with key from below. )))
Press enter.
Done. Reboot.

Nevermind on the script part.  TPB will not allow the code to be displayed.

The script and instructions can be found on micro$soft's web pages.  Just search and you will find it

I've tried this installation out on three different PCs, and it works well assuming you can find a working CD key.

However, this is not an untouched copy. I tried using Nlite on this only to find out there are already Nlite edits applied.

Despite the torrent title, this is not a default, untouched copy of Windows XP Pro SP2.
Clean, untouched and perfect!  Thank you.
